    <note>Lin(1) Lu [15185] His wife was born Lu(1) and his son, Bang [15185], and his grandson, Maochen [15187], both used the surname of Lu(1) and his great grandson, Lin(1) Dazhong [15188] (q.v. for documentation), again took the surname Lin. This is clearly a genuine uxorilocal marriage situation with Dazhong (certainly a younger brother) reestablishing continuity with his agnatic lineage. I am entering both Bang and Maochen as Lu(1), but as members of this lineage.</note>
